snippet.title: THUG PRO: The Definitive Tony Hawk Experience
snippet.description:
Flippy's How to Install 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3oZUfObQ1ys 

THUG PRO Official Site
http://thugpro.com/

Mod THUG PRO on 
www.thpsx.com

Spider-Man 2000 Mods
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QmiIwgB_pVo
======= Join the Discord ! ! !=======
 https://discord.gg/HsYCrqQ
Leave a comment if I need to update the link, then check my latest video's link!
=======Support the Channel=======

Donate to my Ko-Fi and receive your name at the end of a video, and in the description of every Volume 2 video.
 https://ko-fi.com/superswimteam7

Streamlabs Donation:
https://streamlabs.com/superswimteam7

Amazon Wishlist: https://www.amazon.com/registry/wishlist/EE5K9Z795YA1/

Redbubble Store: I plan on developing a more professional merch line if things ever take off, but until then, here are some rad stickers I've designed! https://www.redbubble.com/people/superswimteam7/shop/top+selling+stickers?accordion=product&ref=artist_shop_product_refinement&asc=u

Anyone who helps improve the studio (via ko-fi or Amazon) will get their name in the description and a shout out at the end of a video. Anything helps! Thanks for the support!

=======Vol. 2 KO-FI / Patreon SUPPORTERS========

Thank you very much to 
"Josh Thoughts" https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCSRF...
and
"Mad Moon Magic" 
and
"Blake!"
for supporting me on Ko-Fi!
